title: Ep. 30 Young, Dumb, And....You Know The Rest
description:
Why can't we be young forever? Because we'd be dumb forever.

Big announcements this week!
Plus, United is TRASH, road trips are best with crazy friends and crazier men, and nice cars aren't always driven by good people. Let's all thank God we're not as dumb as were 5 years ago.
